        "parent_id": null,
        "type": "nodetool.input.StringInput",
        "data": {
          "name": "topic",
          "value": "The economics of home solar batteries",
          "description": "Subject the orchestrator should research and write a short explainer about."
        },
        "ui_properties": {
          "selected": false,
          "title": "1️⃣ Topic",
          "position": {
            "x": 40,
            "y": 120
          },
          "zIndex": 0,
          "width": 280,
          "selectable": true
        },
        "dynamic_properties": {},
        "dynamic_outputs": {}
      },
      {
        "id": "brief",
        "parent_id": null,
        "type": "nodetool.text.Prompt",
        "data": {
          "prompt": "Write a concise, accurate explainer (250-350 words) about the following subject:\n\n{{ topic }}\n\nProcess:\n1. Call the research_specialist tool with a focused question about this subject to gather current facts, figures, and context.\n2. Draft the explainer yourself using those facts. Do not invent numbers — rely on what research returns.\n3. Call the copy_editor tool with your draft to tighten the prose and fix tone.\n4. Return the copy editor's polished version as the final answer, as Markdown."
        },
        "ui_properties": {
          "selected": false,
          "title": "2️⃣ Objective",
          "position": {
            "x": 40,
            "y": 320
          },
          "zIndex": 0,
          "width": 280,
          "selectable": true
        },
        "dynamic_properties": {
          "topic": null
        },
        "dynamic_outputs": {}
      },
      {
        "id": "orchestrator",
        "parent_id": null,
        "type": "nodetool.agents.Agent",
        "data": {
          "model": {
            "type": "language_model",
            "provider": "openai",
            "id": "gpt-5-mini",
            "name": "GPT-5 mini",
            "path": null,
            "supported_tasks": []
          },
          "tools": [],
          "max_tokens": 16000,
          "mode": "loop",
          "prompt": "",
          "system": "You are an editorial manager who coordinates specialists rather than doing everything yourself.\n\nYou have two tools, each a specialist agent:\n- research_specialist — give it a single, focused question. It returns facts, figures, and context. Use it before drafting; never invent data.\n- copy_editor — give it a full draft. It returns a tighter, cleaner version. Use it once, on your finished draft.\n\nProcess for every task:\n1. Read the objective and decide what to research.\n2. Call research_specialist with one clear question (pass only the `prompt` argument).\n3. Draft the piece yourself from the returned facts.\n4. Call copy_editor with your draft (pass only the `prompt` argument).\n5. Return the copy editor's polished text verbatim as your final answer.\n\nKeep the final answer in Markdown. Do not describe your tool calls in the answer — just deliver the finished piece."
        },
        "ui_properties": {
          "selected": false,
          "title": "3️⃣ Orchestrator",
